    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can start with <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/time/Instant.html#ofEpochMilli-long-\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Instant.ofEpochMilli(long)</a>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>LocalDate date =\n  Instant.ofEpochMilli(startDateLong)\n  .atZone(ZoneId.systemDefault())\n  .toLocalDate();\n</code></pre>\n"
