      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "@Pryftan “to use the long value of a file last mod date” is a very unspecific task. Are you sure you actually need a <code>LocalDate</code>? Maybe whatever you actually want to do with the long value, can be done with the <code>Instant</code> created via <code>Instant.ofEpochMilli(longValue)</code> too."
