    "body" : "<p>A simple version based on <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/43318605/5006866\">@Michael Piefel answer</a>:</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-java prettyprint-override\"><code>LocalDate myDate = LocalDate.ofEpochDay(Duration.ofMillis(epochMillis).toDays());\n</code></pre>\n"
